{"article_id":"o4QrxQgeFNSWM8Rt","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Washington ( CNN ) -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"A majority of Americans still oppose the nation 's new health care measure ,","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"three years after it became law ,","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"according to a new survey .","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"But a CNN/ORC International poll","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"released Monday","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"also indicates","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"that more than a quarter of those","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"who oppose the law ,","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"known by many as Obamacare ,","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"say","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"they do n't support the measure","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"because it does n't go far enough .","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"According to the poll ,","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"43 % of the public says","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"it supports the health care law , a figure","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"that 's mostly unchanged in CNN polling","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"since the measure was passed in 2010 by a Congress","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"then controlled by Democrats","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"and signed into law by President Barack Obama .","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"Fifty-four percent of those questioned say","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"they oppose the law , also relatively unchanged since 2010 .","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"The survey indicates","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"that 35 % oppose the health care law","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"because it 's too liberal ,","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"with 16 % saying","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"they oppose the measure","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"because it is n't liberal enough .","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"The wide partisan divide over the law remains .","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"Nearly three quarters of Democrats say","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"they favor the Affordable Care Act .","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"That number drops to 16 % among Republicans .","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"`` Not surprisingly , the Obama coalition is most supportive of Obamacare , ''","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"says CNN Polling Director Keating Holland .","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"`` A majority of younger Americans favor the new health care law ;","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"support among other age groups falls as low as 31 % among senior citizens .","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"Only a third of whites support the law ,","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"compared to six in 10 non-whites .","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"Obamacare also wins majority support in urban areas and in the Northeast , the bluest region of the country . ''","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"The CNN poll was conducted May 17-18 ,","depth":4},{"id":40,"text":"right after the GOP-controlled House voted along party lines to repeal the entire law ,","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"the third time","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"House Republicans have voted to overturn the measure over the past three years .","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"As with the previous attempts , the bill is expected to die in the Democrat-controlled Senate .","depth":5},{"id":44,"text":"The survey was conducted by ORC International ,","depth":4},{"id":45,"text":"with 923 adults nationwide questioned by telephone .","depth":4},{"id":46,"text":"The poll 's overall sampling error is plus or minus three percentage points .","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":93,"left":0,"right":92,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":92,"left":89,"right":91,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":89,"left":84,"right":88,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":84,"left":58,"right":83,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":58,"left":49,"right":57,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":49,"left":48,"right":3,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":48,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":57,"left